{"id":523360013,"lang":"cpp","time":"8Â months","timestamp":1626421966,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"8 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/523360013/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Rectangle Area","memory":"5.9 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    int getArea(int x1,int y1,int x2,int y2){\n        return abs(x1-x2)*abs(y1-y2);\n    }\n    int computeArea(int ax1, int ay1, int ax2, int ay2, int bx1, int by1, int bx2, int by2) {\n        int ax=getArea(ax1,ay1,ax2,ay2);\n        int bx=getArea(bx1,by1,bx2,by2);\n        int x1=max(ax1,bx1);\n        int y1=max(ay1,by1);\n        int x2=min(bx2,ax2);\n        int y2=min(by2,ay2);\n        int com=(x2<=x1 || y2<=y1)?0:getArea(x1,y1,x2,y2);\n        return ax+bx-com;\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"rectangle-area"}
